<br>
No offense, but I deserved an alt for my work on FV, my alt was to have fun and be able to do more.  No matter what you do on the server, you will never surpass me, I was here at the beginning, saw the world form and change, was among those of us here who made it what it is.  I was the first to go to North Karana and East Karana, I was probably the first to get to Freeport on the server from Qeynos at level 5.  <br>
<br>
